{"tid":1395813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[麻煩入黎睇,長文]點解唔塞鐵？政府有港鐵75%股份，點解反對派係咁話塞鐵唔會影響到政府？","createTime":"2019-08-02T01:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T04:00:20.000Z","uid":15371,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a76695cc401daa645efd43e61f9e25e299c55d","tid":1395813,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:17:02.000Z","msg":"我真係唔太明到底係真心定五毛<br />\n影響民生？睇返甘地不合作運動咪又係一樣大把野影響民生<br />\n得罪講句，奴性最重既黃種人真係好難會主動罷工，反而塞鐵可以令佢被動罷工、有藉口<br />\n.<br />\n所謂得失取捨<br />\n今日示威既成本已經越黎越貴<br />\n暴動罪係入去坐十年<br />\n至於塞鐵既成本係最平，同時符合真正既不合作運動果種和平理性非暴力又有效果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b6e0ZYT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb6e0ZYT.png&h=db3c8924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n.<br />\n如果你係真心講反對塞鐵既，我唔該你地，去睇下甘地不合作運動，GOOGLE下就有<br />\n再唔係，就睇下高質節目，睇下歷史學家點樣講呢方面<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-1DUyalf1wY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-1DUyalf1wY&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFEPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=f025bf68\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-1DUyalf1wY</a><br />\n[五夜講場 - 歷史係咁話 2019：以暴抗暴真勇武？]<br />\n.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gNnh2b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgNnh2b8.jpg&h=980a77ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府有港鐵75%股份<br />\n點解會唔影響政府？五毛成日用「高官自己揸車論」<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J4caCMr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4caCMr.jpg&h=7b432715&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n都係果句啦，參考下甘地既不合作運動<br />\n講多都無謂<br />\n成日都話民眾打民眾<br />\n順便比多條高質片你睇下其實政府目前做緊乜<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2cMQAIp9kjU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2cMQAIp9kjU&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFEPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=ebf36b4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2cMQAIp9kjU</a><br />\n[港豬與港犬 | 極權下的精神病 | 港式犬儒主義]<br />\n佢宜家已經做到兩邊對立，你覺得真係仲有中立？<br />\n可能有既，所以更加需要文宣，好多人根本唔知不合作運動既本質<br />\n.<br />\n最後<br />\n希望大家可以堅持<br />\n革命從來唔會係一蹴而就既事情"},{"pid":"2016a9671c6c7bb9e0b7ad1e9325ead24c5f2710","tid":1395813,"uid":15371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:27:10.000Z","msg":"去示威，就算好彩無比人當場拉，你又要擔心事後比人拉，就算真係無比警察拉都好，係前線就食警棍食催淚彈食呢樣果樣、甚至流血<br />\n就算前線再勇武，你打低警察，一樣會比藍絲話<br />\n而且仲會被控襲警、暴動<br />\n.<br />\n宜家真係有和平理性非暴力既不合作運動，仲要唔驚比警察拉<br />\n無論你真心定五毛都好，我都好想聽下你地到底點解反對塞鐵<br />\n請出招<br />\n<br />\n順便自推"},{"pid":"ec151864958cc49b8b1bbf3ed3c7752fa3b1eff7","tid":1395813,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:11:20.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"126a54a04ba327d759b15ee7e90c7dbe7b8a3839","tid":1395813,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:12:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"67ef8eeb87a504d93635062b378a92a884580359","tid":1395813,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:15:13.000Z","msg":"班柒頭返遲1秒工會死"},{"pid":"73f23b1237c40c3ce175a3e6c02306128753631c","tid":1395813,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:42:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"112c9c57def7359917e5ac908c7999aa2fa172af","tid":1395813,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:42:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b41962fb1e011a9aa522e2f65cf1dfbc13758aff","tid":1395813,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:43:04.000Z","msg":"好少好認真咁係連登打呢類既文<br />\n但今次真係忍唔住手"},{"pid":"a67bcf4cd8f80431d5ffa850be3fe42d2cc36221","tid":1395813,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:43:40.000Z","msg":"#罷工罷巿罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我會參與8月5日全港三罷<br />\n#七區集會<br />\n#直至政府跪低"},{"pid":"80fbef6bf3fbec6854158174914ab9e6296708b3","tid":1395813,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:14:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c9cc1cf10e7a5379c16a9e43d2bd32a062c34adc","tid":1395813,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:41:21.000Z","